<section class="get-started">
  <h1>Get Started with SubSense</h1>

  <h2>Free Tier Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Track up to 5 subscriptions</li>
    <li>Basic analytics: total spend & next billing date</li>
    <li>Category filtering & search</li>
    <li>Standard renewal reminders</li>
    <li>Local data storage & manual iCloud backup</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Premium Tier Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Unlimited subscriptions</li>
    <li>Advanced analytics & cost optimization</li>
    <li>Personalized recommendations to save money</li>
    <li>Export to CSV/PDF & custom themes/icons</li>
    <li>Family sharing & priority customer support</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Subscription Plans</h2>
  <p>Choose monthly or annual billing (annual plan includes optional free trial and discounted rate).</p>

  <h2>How to Add Your First Subscription</h2>
  <p>Tap “Add Subscription”, fill in the name, billing date, and cost, then save to start tracking.</p>

